   Politics &amp; Policy:
   Bush Declines
   To Take Steps
   Against Soviets
   ---
   President Hopes Lithuania
   Can Start Negotiating,
   Cites Allies' Reluctance
   ----
   By Gerald F. Seib
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
